item.title: CVE-2023-2578|2024-08-02T06:26:09.814Z -- unknown -- buy%20me%20a%20coffee
item.description: The Buy Me a Coffee WordPress plugin before 3.7 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed (for example in multisite setup).
